Title: Labia Majora
Plot: Bette and Tina deal with parenting Angelica while attempting to rekindle their relationship and handle an obnoxious social worker. Alice has a traffic accident, Helena gets into the movie business, Carmen and Shane's relationship gets more serious as Carmen takes her to meet the parents, and Jenny, recovering at her parents', has had enough with the Midwest and ponders moving back to L.A. with her new girlfriend Moira.
GuestStars: Cynthia Stevenson,  Tamara Prescott,  Leanna Nash,  Marilyn Norry,  Annabel Kershaw,  Kate Clinton,  Colin Lawrence,  Paralee Cook,  Margot Kidder,  Michelle Candido,  Esmeralda Fortin,  Patricia Mayen-Salazar
